  <p>A smile simulator can be a helpful first step when you are curious about cosmetic dentistry but not ready to choose a treatment. Uploading a clear smile photo gives you a visual starting point for a conversation with Elm Ridge Implant and Family Dentistry in Killeen.</p>
  <p>The preview is not meant to replace a dental exam. It is a planning tool. Real cosmetic treatment depends on tooth position, enamel, bite forces, gum levels, existing restorations, budget, and long-term health.</p>
